ed that the demand for water will double till FY 2030 and it this demand is not met, then there would be crash of 6% in GDP of India. So to tackle this issue, PM Modi is laying emphasis on conserving water.", "002-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://www.insightsonindia.com/2019/06/03/jal-shaktimunistry/"}}